metadata.name: Iconic Fractal Pt.2 #1
metadata.description: Iconic Fractals Part 2 are created by an AI algorithm that takes fractals and creates new pieces in the styles of famous artists. The collection includes pieces created by our AI in the style of Pieter Bruegel, Yayoi Kusama, Piet Mondria, Matisse, Andy Warhol, Klimt and Paul Cezanne.
